{"tid":906052,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"RDR2 全爆機[[隱藏]]溝女劇情 有圖有真相","createTime":"2018-11-17T15:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T22:37:37.000Z","uid":189729,"like":6,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fcda396d5103d47c05203c50e07071882781d053","tid":906052,"uid":189729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T15:52:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/ZgCcoLCvMky5zq2s9boDUA/0_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net%2Fugc%2Frdr2photo%2FZgCcoLCvMky5zq2s9boDUA%2F0_0.jpg&h=a23a95a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/scpDltWxKUCLumtRoBnQTg/0_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net%2Fugc%2Frdr2photo%2FscpDltWxKUCLumtRoBnQTg%2F0_0.jpg&h=2a0fe945&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去到酒吧見到條女,佢好悶一個人,<br />\n<img src=\"https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/AumGEERkCEWP4Y7d7_g3jQ/0_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net%2Fugc%2Frdr2photo%2FAumGEERkCEWP4Y7d7_g3jQ%2F0_0.jpg&h=26be66b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我話佢出去行下,佢話OK<br />\n<img src=\"https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/xKYhtYUT40SSLEE9-pTDxg/0_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net%2Fugc%2Frdr2photo%2FxKYhtYUT40SSLEE9-pTDxg%2F0_0.jpg&h=d8e94d0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於我係新手唔識路,佢等左我好耐<br />\n<a href=\"https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/gzsursBsZ0COPeunEs6qRw/0_0.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net%2Fugc%2Frdr2photo%2FgzsursBsZ0COPeunEs6qRw%2F0_0.jpg&d=Ao7t8yvT3hs8ulZu38hyojQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a153e0e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/gzsursBsZ0COPeunEs6qRw/0_0.jpg</a><br />\n佢有D心急<br />\n<img src=\"https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/scr3np9o8Eq1KmRZrbztSA/0_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net%2Fugc%2Frdr2photo%2Fscr3np9o8Eq1KmRZrbztSA%2F0_0.jpg&h=8b2c46d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我一出現佢即刻開心晒<br />\n<img src=\"https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/Fg5b8lJGI0K0nScn1W2fpw/0_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net%2Fugc%2Frdr2photo%2FFg5b8lJGI0K0nScn1W2fpw%2F0_0.jpg&h=5ca76367&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/Z7EDzwD9yk2L9EKtebPbug/0_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net%2Fugc%2Frdr2photo%2FZ7EDzwD9yk2L9EKtebPbug%2F0_0.jpg&h=dc59df59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n傾完一輪佢話聽日見,當中佢有D唔愿意透露 佢係做小姐<br />\n<img src=\"https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/zeGTsOLaLUiJ7uYWyFr22A/0_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net%2Fugc%2Frdr2photo%2FzeGTsOLaLUiJ7uYWyFr22A%2F0_0.jpg&h=407a8d66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第2日我見佢接第2個客,佢好驚訝見到我搵佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/8uR9TARWqUiWrbD_BcFvBg/0_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net%2Fugc%2Frdr2photo%2F8uR9TARWqUiWrbD_BcFvBg%2F0_0.jpg&h=1888c2ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢唔9采我<br />\n<img src=\"https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/0WqQUntkPUaJnqnsrbCGqw/0_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net%2Fugc%2Frdr2photo%2F0WqQUntkPUaJnqnsrbCGqw%2F0_0.jpg&h=e6a502f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲嘈左一輪<br />\n<img src=\"https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/teR18yeoKEK7X9OvFfORQQ/0_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net%2Fugc%2Frdr2photo%2FteR18yeoKEK7X9OvFfORQQ%2F0_0.jpg&h=03a318da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我決定佢收工跟住佢,想同佢講清楚<br />\n<img src=\"https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/gq1Gtzr-JEKnv_9nYYPUjw/0_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net%2Fugc%2Frdr2photo%2Fgq1Gtzr-JEKnv_9nYYPUjw%2F0_0.jpg&h=b1689123&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟到去後巷,忍唔住綁走左佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/TUXUn4OMS0SbWNRXTpbsOA/0_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net%2Fugc%2Frdr2photo%2FTUXUn4OMS0SbWNRXTpbsOA%2F0_0.jpg&h=11356769&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n帶左佢去間廢屋,再姦左佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/WGojX0kxAUKZY9ELicJfDw/0_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net%2Fugc%2Frdr2photo%2FWGojX0kxAUKZY9ELicJfDw%2F0_0.jpg&h=fd061fbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/z9dktw8390q7JpQgraeGSg/0_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net%2Fugc%2Frdr2photo%2Fz9dktw8390q7JpQgraeGSg%2F0_0.jpg&h=04fc3ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過程佢反抗<br />\n<img src=\"https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/LJI7cMUJZEKwkhjDYOBc-g/0_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net%2Fugc%2Frdr2photo%2FLJI7cMUJZEKwkhjDYOBc-g%2F0_0.jpg&h=88b5051d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/xQ5bQJ3hq0WD-qjXvM1_VQ/0_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net%2Fugc%2Frdr2photo%2FxQ5bQJ3hq0WD-qjXvM1_VQ%2F0_0.jpg&h=f87cb415&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n玩到室外<br />\n<img src=\"https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/aAguPOIrSkiHj2W-Xv22Pg/0_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net%2Fugc%2Frdr2photo%2FaAguPOIrSkiHj2W-Xv22Pg%2F0_0.jpg&h=eb4367c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/ZolSpoW7p0ezzFK5tlG9oQ/0_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net%2Fugc%2Frdr2photo%2FZolSpoW7p0ezzFK5tlG9oQ%2F0_0.jpg&h=6983648d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢突然撞穿個頭死左<br />\n<img src=\"https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/QzcKMH9j-keu9taP219CoA/0_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net%2Fugc%2Frdr2photo%2FQzcKMH9j-keu9taP219CoA%2F0_0.jpg&h=276456f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n埋左佢又驚比人發現<br />\n<img src=\"https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/Bvbq34pMLUadNJmZ7yrHzg/0_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net%2Fugc%2Frdr2photo%2FBvbq34pMLUadNJmZ7yrHzg%2F0_0.jpg&h=ecc83486&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/FMlsM8H620G1Ts9_91zozw/0_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net%2Fugc%2Frdr2photo%2FFMlsM8H620G1Ts9_91zozw%2F0_0.jpg&h=28230c12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我決定斬碎佢諗住沖走佢,但唔WORK<br />\n<img src=\"https://prod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net/ugc/rdr2photo/pr05rUOI-ki0pgEaluMvAA/0_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprod-cdnugc-rockstargames.akamaized.net%2Fugc%2Frdr2photo%2Fpr05rUOI-ki0pgEaluMvAA%2F0_0.jpg&h=0461f087&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後屋都燒埋當一場意外"},{"pid":"a8ebef54ada91899a0769f4d